Author: BronArianwyn
Text: Maybe, im usually so bad about reaching out like that.   i'd be so down but if its just a new thing....i dont wanna drag her in here with us.  I want her to shake it off. My personal experience has made me into a dismal dark jokster about it if i ever do mention it at all.  mostly cause when you tell some one you aint eaten in 4 days and they dont give a shit why bother telling anyone anything at all LOL

Author: 5mokahontas
Text: the constant mentioning of not eating *sounds* like a cry for help or some type of attention. not in a bad way, just like “someone please notice I’m not okay” type of way? idk, I’m just going by personal experience. or she’s trying to find someone else w/ similar eating habits? like she’s trying to find a friend to relate with?
